MIRIAD “Medical Instruction and Retrieval Dataset”dataset :

 📂Dataset: https://lnkd.in/e4qVkg_k
 🔗Website: https://lnkd.in/e5jWhBxW
 📜Preprint: https://lnkd.in/e7yFj2SX
 💻Code: https://lnkd.in/ekGSKDrN
 🪐Demo: https://lnkd.in/eafUEFzn


Description :
5,821,948 medical instruction-response pairs drawn from Seamantic Scholar papers
Spans 56 medical disciplines
6.7% LLM precision increase
22.5 to 37% improvement of hallucination detection

Pros
✅ Open source HuggingFace repository
✅ Clear question/answer format
✅ Paper and text passage cited for each answer (verifiable and reproductible)
✅ Only medical questions/answers
✅ Large range of medical fields consulted

Cons
🚫 No automatic test/train split on repository
🚫 Only in English : no translation examples or results



